ğŸ”¹ How the System Works

1. User enters ATM Number & PIN.


2. If authenticated, user can:

View Balance

Deposit Cash

Withdraw Cash

View Mini Statement



3. System logs each transaction using a HashMap.


4. Clean exit from the system.




